text: Intel Core i9 12900K is a 12th generation Intel Core processors. It has 16 cores and 24 threads. It is based on big.LITTLE design. The 8 cores are performance-focused, running at 3.2 GHz. The other 8 cores are efficiency- focused, running at 2.4 GHz. It also has 30 MB cache. Category:Intel Core processors
title: Intel Core i9 12900K
